stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Instantiated : create Shape
    Instantiated --> Idle : add to Diagram + redraw
    Idle --> Selected : on_canvas_click()
    Selected --> Dragging : on_canvas_drag()
    Dragging --> Dropped : on_canvas_release()
    Dropped --> Idle : snap_to_grid
    Selected --> Idle : click elsewhere / deselect
    Selected --> Deleted : delete_selected()
    Idle --> Deleted : delete (reversible command)
    Deleted --> [*]
